Package: prsr
Title: Calculate PRS Using Plink
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Levin", , "michael.levin@pennmedicine.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9937-9932"))
Description: A set of functions that use plink2 to calculate polygenic
    risk scores (PRS) on a target dataset given a base dataset that
    includes variants, effect alleles, and corresponding weights.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mglev1n/prsr, https://mglev1n.github.io/prsr/
